[hr 
]hr
[h3 
	"About the game
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Romansing SaGa is RPG released by Square(famous for Final Fantasy series) in 1992.
	$LF
	"It is the 4th work of SaGa series. It was released only in Japan. 
	$LF
	"SaGa series are popular in Japan as much as Final Fantasy series. 
	$LF
	"Romansing SaGa is the first work that adopts "Free scenario system" in the series. 
	$LF
	"First of all, the player chooses the hero from 8 characters.
	$LF
	"The first state is different depending on the hero whom the player chose. 
	$LF
	"However, The final purpose of any hero is the same.  
	$LF
	"The player can choose the scenario freely by the goal.
	$LF
]p
[hr 
]hr
[h3 
	"About the glitch
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"It is famous in Romancing SaGa that there are a lot of glitches.
	$LF
	"In this run, I used the glitch named "Lady-luck's Bug"(LB). 
	$LF
	"Only when Hawk is a hero, LB can be used.   
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The occurrence condition of LB is as follows. 
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		"Reperts "Enters Oapu → Driven out from Oapu" 10 times.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"The phenomenon generated by LB includes many things. 
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Typical phenomena are as follows.
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		"Speaks an unknown thing.  
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Moves to another map.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Specific items are obtained.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Specific characters become companions. 
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Suddenly starts a battle with the last boss. 
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"What phenomenon happens changes in the timing of the key input.It changes in each frame. 
	$LF
	"In this run, I cause phenomenon "Suddenly starts ending" by luck manipulation.
	$LF
	""Suddenly starts ending" is a very unusual phenomenon.
	$LF
]p
